steps.description: Summarize the search results to extract a list of smartphone models.

tool_arguments.code:
search_results = duckduckgo_search_results("latest smartphone models", 5)
import re
models = re.findall(r'(Pixel \d+[a-zA-Z]*|Google Pixel \d+ Pro|Apple iPhone \d+|Samsung Galaxy S\d+ Ultra)', str(search_results))
result = f"Latest smartphone models: {', '.join(models) if models else 'No models found'}"
return result
